high_descs: Turn around and move toward the white table in front of you.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Turn around and move to the sink on the left.
Place the butter knife into the cup in the sink.
Pick up the cup with the butter knife inside.
Move to the counter attached to the right side of the sink.
Place the cup with the butter knife inside onto the right counter.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the butter knife and glass cup to place them on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left then walk forward then turn left again to the table.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Turn around completely and then turn to the left and walk towards the sink
Place the butter knife in the wine glass that is inside the sink.
Pick up the glass and knife from the sink.
Turn to the right and face the counter.
Place the knife and wine glass on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a wine glass and butter knife to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around to your left then face the table on your right
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the knife in the glass
Pick up the glass with knife at the sink
Turn right then face the counter
Put the glass with knife on the right side of the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the glass with knife on the right side of the counter
